{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7fa8467411","title":"金怀鹏档案之二：肃反调查材料","origin":"根据档案材料翻印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3c126ed47d","index":0,"year":1955,"month":9,"day":11,"articleId":"7fa8467411"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ef5a9de107","type":"title","text":"金怀鹏档案之二：肃反调查材料","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"e52a9ff2bd","type":"subtitle","text":"调查材料","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"b9c6a9e4f7","type":"paragraph","text":"金怀鹏","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"3241485a6d","type":"paragraph","text":"社会关系复杂","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"aff3e7bee9","type":"paragraph","text":"大哥金怀禹，国民党员、三青团员、青工队员（特务组织），曾干过伪职等","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"5594e45762","type":"paragraph","text":"表哥杨诚愚，干过商会会长","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"c1d17233b4","type":"paragraph","text":"舅舅，阎文光，三番（安青帮）收过徒弟","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"6b84bb141f","type":"subtitle","text":"关于金怀鹏的材料调查报告","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"337d403f62","type":"paragraph","text":"根据多方的了解证明金怀鹏的社会关系是复杂的。他大哥金怀禹过去在伪方参加过国民党员、青工队（特务组织），他舅父参加过安庆帮收过学生，他表兄干过保长。金怀鹏那时是与他们是有联系的，在最近还与他哥哥有联系，寄信给家了解统购统销的情况，要他哥哥告诉他家里的粮食供应情况。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"2f41a1d26b","type":"appellation","text":"另外关于金怀鹏是否参加三青团，根据调查了解是没有参加三青团。因那时他在家年龄很小，他在巢县中学时才只有13、4岁，同时那时已经是48年秋天了，入学后3个月的时间巢县就解放了。根据在公安局的调查，公安局也有巢县中学的三青团的材料，从这几方面看来，金怀鹏是没有参加三青团的组织，这是我个人的分析。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"b5f6a0ddb4","type":"paragraph","text":"附证明材料3份","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"bcede14ecb","type":"paragraph","text":" 调查材料人　王鸿斗 09.11","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"855aaedf18","type":"subtitle","text":"金怀鹏家庭成份的材料","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"f06ef7771b","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）家庭成份系小土地出租，计田8亩多的，现已全部出卖，房屋计有7间半。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"e485ad4818","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）社会关系：大哥金怀禹解放前任过伪巢县参议会秘书、司法科录事、秘书科科员，曾参加国民党员、三青团员、青工队员（特务组织。）","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"3d88c4fe83","type":"paragraph","text":"表哥杨诚愚干过伪拓皋商会主席。舅舅阎文光干过三番（安庆帮）","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"77cab62e06","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）金怀鹏在家时常和表兄、大哥、舅父联系，解放后也常有信联系，并于最近期间的来信询问家中粮食统购统销和供应情况，并叫他大哥写信告诉他。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"c7fd4c513d","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）关于金怀鹏在家没有参加过三青团和反动组织，但在学校内情况不明。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"ce986a5f2f","type":"paragraph","text":" 调查人　王鸿斗拓皋十一选区　李献珊　郑贵才 09.11","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"19cb3e1efb","type":"paragraph","text":"该材料确实","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"c4d78cfecd","type":"paragraph","text":" 褚长真　中共拓皋镇支部书记","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"648c2fd2c9","type":"paragraph","text":"同意大家意见","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"443d4da9aa","type":"paragraph","text":" 中国共产党巢县拓皋区委员会","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"ed068bae4f","type":"subtitle","text":"金怀鹏的亲戚情况","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"51c46476e3","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）阎文光是金怀鹏的舅舅，其阎文光本人曾在上海替外国人纱厂看门，一度自己开设炭店，并收了若干帮会学生，胜利后来过拓皋，同时在拓皋买了一座房子，（现在阎文光已死，只有阎的老婆及一个儿子、三个女儿）。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"9034603c5c","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）杨诚愚是金怀鹏的老表，其杨诚愚本人一向做生意，于1940年任伪紫金保保长，并担任过伪拓皋镇商会会长。在解放后51年曾被管制半年。现其本人仍在开店。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"f8e316d675","type":"paragraph","text":" 反映人：张元荣、程国炳、秦忠才亲笔于55年9月11日","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"b827e6e5aa","type":"appellation","text":"滁县盐业公司：","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"492c9fc4d4","type":"paragraph","text":"兹证明你司王鸿斗同志于本（9）月9日来我处查对金怀鹏三青团材料，经查找我处无此人材料，特此证明是实。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"1d7e1b5b09","type":"paragraph","text":"致以","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"9d73bbd43c","type":"appellation","text":"敬礼","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"},{"id":"7f7c314b57","type":"paragraph","text":" 巢县人民政府公安局","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411"}],"page":{"id":"b4a3b420c9","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7fa8467411","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}